                    <div class="text-xs text-gray-500">**Herramientas:** Modeling, Texture, Lightning, Render, Sound.</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Proyecto 4: CRC Interactive Model -->
            <div class="project-card md:col-span-1">
                <img src="http://googleusercontent.com/image_collection/image_retrieval/17696434491740928731" alt="Modelo Interactivo CRC" class="project-image">
